cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use or reference Sprout, please cite it."
title: "Sprout"
abstract: >-
  Sprout is an open-source plant-care assistant that lets each plant tell you how it's
  doing, in its own words: a local-first ESP32 soil-moisture monitor and small-pump waterer
  reading capacitive sensors into calibrated bands, paired with host tooling and a
  zero-friction contributor setup.
type: software
authors:
